{"tid":1544966,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"今日一件小事令我覺得香港人係會贏","createTime":"2019-09-05T17:39:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T19:16:23.000Z","uid":81993,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"68377bdb0f4f241b7718a7a764d9b0fa3f28b7e0","tid":1544966,"uid":81993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:39:44.000Z","msg":"身為沙田友既我，見到今晚沙田突發人鏈 ，當然要參加啦。<br />\n但我落樓梯嗰陣唔小心將成個AirPods 跌左落地下，有一邊仲跌左落一個好深既草叢入面，咁當時梗係無執啦，大事要緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n終於等到活動完結，我同我個fd 試下去搵啦，個下都覺得好似香港咁絕望，真係有諗過放棄，算啦唔要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n途中有幾位手足都主動問我洗唔洗幫手，我都話唔使啦，因為係咁黑既環境下，我自己都覺得搵唔到，搵到既機會仲細過香港救得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知，竟然係好深好大既草叢見到好細粒既AirPod earphone，即刻大叫有無巴打幫手，有幾個熱心既巴打幫我照，我最尾終於搵得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個下我真心覺得香港人呢次一定會贏，因為我都可以係咁黑既環境，咁大片既草叢搵到粒earphone，個機會率一定低過香港人贏呢一場仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以香港人加油 一個都不能少<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n期待大家係煲底除罩相見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"155416969e2dc192c06dc0f4c6e0fad1150bb4ff","tid":1544966,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:40:06.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":