a-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fabda81119e3d2415415907c24ff9f4f8c7e0a49","tid":1544966,"uid":81993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:43:06.000Z","msg":"還香港人831真相"},{"pid":"acc725992f87f026b6e4bebdda93d1bc20dcfd46","tid":1544966,"uid":260036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:45:39.000Z","msg":"又話好憎禿鷹嘅你哋？ <br />\n推咗成日簽得萬幾個？ 撞鬼呀？<br />\n<br />\n【白宮網終於郁返】<br />\n<br />\n快啲簽咗呢個先。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-reject-nomination-andy-tsang-wai-hung-positions-united-nations\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-reject-nomination-andy-tsang-wai-hung-positions-united-nations&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWNE6lK5ze4L1B2G6UiHaG78%3D&h=5b7e4d6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-reject-nomination-andy-tsang-wai-hung-positions-united-nations</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6rpEGXU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6rpEGXU.jpg&h=f77d4459&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9fac827c025f4260957eec39738dbc8a03b0e225","tid":1544966,"uid":162516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:51:27.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個草叢咁深都揾到 香港一定有救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"ef9e33844edc2fd17d272e5efb62b829bf9da7f1","tid":1544966,"uid":94968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:57:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.